items.headline: Panthers at Rangers preview
items.subhead: Rangers seek third straight win; Huberdeau looks to extend point streak for Florida
items.seoTitle: Florida Panthers New York Rangers Game Preview
items.seoDescription: The New York Rangers seek their first three-game winning streak of the season when they host the Florida Panthers at Madison Square Garden on Sunday.
items.seoKeywords: NHL, Hockey, Game Preview, Florida Panthers, New York Rangers, Henrik Lundqvist
items.preview:
PANTHERS (7-4-5) at RANGERS (7-6-1)

1 p.m. ET; NHLN, MSG, FS-F, NHL.TV

 

The Game

The New York Rangers seek their first three-game winning streak of the season when they host the Florida Panthers at Madison Square Garden on Sunday.

items.headline: Panthers rally to defeat Rangers in shootout
items.subhead: Trocheck scores deciding goal, Dadonov has three points for Florida
items.seoTitle: Florida Panthers New York Rangers Game Recap
items.seoDescription: Evgenii Dadonov had a goal and two assists for the Florida Panthers in a 6-5 shootout win against the New York Rangers at Madison Square Garden on Sunday.
items.seoKeywords: NHL, Hockey, News, Game Recap, Florida Panthers, New York Rangers, overtime, shootout, Vincent Trocheck, Evgenii Dadonov

items.preview: NEW YORK -- Evgenii Dadonov had a goal and two assists for the Florida Panthers in a come-from-behind 6-5 shootout win against the New York Rangers at Madison Square Garden on Sunday.
